    <description>
        <p>Switchfin is third-party PC player for Jellyfin that designed specifically for controller users to browse and play movies and series.</p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Completely native interface</li>
            <li>Supported media items: movies, series, seasons, episodes</li>
            <li>Base on MPV Player</li>
            <li>Filter: Quickly find the movie and bangumi</li>
            <li>Search: TV style, Videos and Movie...</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
